Hi Minoo,

There is access to just one username with the IMMAN package ?jafarilab?. You cannot gain access through ?Minoo-Ashtiani? as it checks for the SSH key and knows there is one user already registered with that key.

I would suggest everyone in the lab, submit changes to https://github.com/jafarilab/IMMAN. And then, sync the GitHub repo with git.bioconductor.org:packages/IMMAN using the ?jafarilab? account. This way, there credential management is handled entirely from your end.

Otherwise, I?d have to give you access rights and you?d have to set up new SSH keys again. 

Best,

Nitesh 



